\v 3 (4) Behold, I am about to <a name="01400200300006" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000:Exist">build</a> a <a name="01400200300008" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000:Buildings" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20140917;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a">house</a> for the <a name="01400200300012" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000003:Self">name</a> of the <a name="01400200300014" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000:Names of Deities">Lord</a> my <a name="01400200300016" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001:Deities">God</a> and <a name="01400200300020" ll="SDBH:קדשׁ:000001:Holy">dedicate</a> it to him for the <a name="01400200300026" ll="SDBH:קטר:000000:Sacrifice" il="HK00260;Realia:4.2.4b;LB00263;NBGlo20140504;Bolen00444;AT Image00600;Realia0086;Realia0087">burning</a> of <a name="01400200300032" ll="SDBH:קְטֹרֶת:000001:Spices" il="HK00260;Realia:4.2.4b;LB00263;Realia:4.4.7.1;NBGlo20140504;NBGbs20100403-1_17;Bolen00444;AT Image00600;Realia0086;Realia0087">incense</a> of <a name="01400200300034" ll="SDBH:סַם:000000:Spices">sweet</a> <a name="01400200300034" ll="SDBH:סַם:000000:Spices">spices</a> <a name="01400200300030">before</a> him, and for the <a name="01400200300040" ll="SDBH:תָּמִיד:000000:Lasting">continual</a> offering of the <a name="01400200300038" ll="SDBH:מַעֲרֶכֶת:000000:Arrange">showbread</a>, and for <a name="01400200300044" ll="SDBH:עֹלָה:000000:Sacrifice" il="HK00256;LB00255;HK00251;LB00254;LB00253;Realia:4.2.3;NBGlo20140504a;NBGlo20140504b;NBGlo20140504c">burnt</a> <a name="01400200300044" ll="SDBH:עֹלָה:000000:Sacrifice" il="HK00256;LB00255;HK00251;LB00254;LB00253;Realia:4.2.3;NBGlo20140504a;NBGlo20140504b;NBGlo20140504c">offerings</a> <a name="01400200300050" ll="SDBH:בֹּקֶר:000000:Time">morning</a> and <a name="01400200300058" ll="SDBH:עֶרֶב:000000:Time">evening</a>, on the <a name="01400200300064" ll="SDBH:שַׁבָּת:000000:Time">sabbaths</a> and the <a name="01400200300072" ll="SDBH:חֹדֶשׁ:000001:Festivals" il="New_moon;Bolen00192;AT Image00536">new</a> <a name="01400200300072" ll="SDBH:חֹדֶ